        "authorId" : "f1480a85-4082-46f9-89c6-fe7231733b83",
        "body" : "No, when SSL is configured on the server, the `SSLUtils::createServerSideSslContextFactory` method is used to create the SSL context factory which should enable hostname verification.\r\nIf the leader has to contact a follower it'll use its own `RestClient` and communicate with the follower's `RestServer` which will be able to perform hostname verification.",
